## 📄 `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# Binaries
airmouse-server
*.exe
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib

# Test binary
*.test

# Output of the go coverage tool
*.out

# Dependency directories
vendor/

# Go workspace file
go.work
go.work.sum

# IDE
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Config (optional – keep example)
config.json
airmouse.log

# Models
models/*.onnx
models/*.pth